    "A British team also engaged in measuring and drawing Greek architecture had only left a few weeks before, that of <a href=\"/stuartj\">James Stuart</a> and Nicholas Revett (1720-1804).": [],
    "Le Roy first went on Delos, then to Athens where he spent several months, and finally Corinth and Sparta, before returning to Paris in 1755.": [
